    <entry>
      <title>秒杀系统</title>
      <link href="/2020/10/10/%E7%A7%92%E6%9D%80/"/>
      <url>/2020/10/10/%E7%A7%92%E6%9D%80/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、设计"><a href="#一、设计" class="headerlink" title="一、设计"></a>一、设计</h2><p>库存预热：<br>提前把商品添加到redis中，整个秒杀流程都在redis中操作，秒杀结束，在异步去修改库存。  </p><p>用户下单：<br>为了提升下单速度，将订单存放的redis中，用户支付后，再将订单存到mysql中，并清空redis中的订单。  </p><p>创建订单：<br>用户每次下单的时候，使用rabbitMQ创建一个队列，采用异步的方式创建订单，从rabbitMQ中读取信息，创建订单。  </p><p>下单状态：<br>做一个页面的判断，每个1s查询下单状态。    </p><p>超卖问题：<br>数据库添加唯一索引，减库存的时候先进行库存数量判断；用redis来维护库存，redis中的库存不足则秒杀失败；异步队列处理订单。  </p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="二、缓存"><a href="#二、缓存" class="headerlink" title="二、缓存"></a>二、缓存</h2><p>在高并发的情况下必然会遇到<strong>缓存雪崩</strong>、<strong>缓存击穿</strong>、<strong>缓存穿透</strong>等问题。而且秒杀是<strong>读多写少</strong>，使用redis作为缓存非常合适（为了避免redis服务器出问题，可以使用redis集群）。  </p><h3 id="2-1、缓存穿透"><a href="#2-1、缓存穿透" class="headerlink" title="2.1、缓存穿透"></a>2.1、缓存穿透</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">描述：</span><br><span class="line">是指缓存和数据库中没有数据，而用户不断请求，会导致数据库压力过大</span><br><span class="line">解决方案：  </span><br><span class="line">1、在接口层校验，如果用户鉴权校验，id为基础校验，id&lt;=0的直接拦截</span><br><span class="line">2、从缓存取不到数据，在数据库中也没有取到，可以将key-value对写成key-null，将缓存有效时间可以设置短点，设置太长会导致无法正常使用。</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="2-2、缓存击穿"><a href="#2-2、缓存击穿" class="headerlink" title="2.2、缓存击穿"></a>2.2、缓存击穿</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">描述：</span><br><span class="line">是指缓存中没有数据但是数据库中有数据（一般是缓存时间到期），这是由于并发用户特别多，同时读缓存没有读到数据，有同时去请求数据库，引起数据库压力瞬间增大。</span><br><span class="line">解决方案：</span><br><span class="line">1、设置热点永不过期</span><br><span class="line">2、加互斥锁</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public String getData(String key) throws InterruptedException {</span><br><span class="line">    // 创建锁</span><br><span class="line">    ReentrantLock reenLock = new ReentrantLock();</span><br><span class="line">    // 从缓存中读取数据</span><br><span class="line">    String result = getDataFromRedis(key);</span><br><span class="line">    // 缓存中不存在数据</span><br><span class="line">    if (result == null){</span><br><span class="line">        // 获取锁，获取成功去数据库中取数据</span><br><span class="line">        if (reenLock.tryLock()){</span><br><span class="line">            // 从数据库获取数据</span><br><span class="line">            result = getDataFromMysql(key);</span><br><span class="line">            // 更新缓存</span><br><span class="line">            if (result != null){</span><br><span class="line">                setDataToCache(key,result);</span><br><span class="line">            }</span><br><span class="line">            // 释放锁</span><br><span class="line">            reenLock.unlock();</span><br><span class="line">        }else{</span><br><span class="line">            // 暂停一会，在重新去获取</span><br><span class="line">            Thread.sleep(100);</span><br><span class="line">            result = getData(key);</span><br><span class="line">        }</span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line">    return result;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="2-3、缓存雪崩"><a href="#2-3、缓存雪崩" class="headerlink" title="2.3、缓存雪崩"></a>2.3、缓存雪崩</h3><pre><code>描述：    是指缓存中数据大量到过期时间，而查询数据量巨大，引起数据库压力过大甚至宕机解决方案：    1、缓存数据的过期时间设置随机，防止同一时间大量数据过期。    2、缓存数据库是分布式部署，将热点数据均匀分布不同缓存数据库中    3、设置热点数据永不过期</code></pre><h2 id="三、削峰-x2F-限流"><a href="#三、削峰-x2F-限流" class="headerlink" title="三、削峰/限流"></a>三、削峰/限流</h2><p>秒杀流量在某一时刻非常高，让瞬间进来的流量进到一个缓存池，然后进行平缓处理（mq消息队列处理）。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@Configuration</span><br><span class="line">public class RabbitConfig {</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    private static final Logger logger = LoggerFactory.getLogger(RabbitConfig.class);</span><br><span class="line">    // 交换机</span><br><span class="line">    public final static String EXCHANGE_NAME = "order:mq:exchange";</span><br><span class="line">    // 队列</span><br><span class="line">    public final static String QUEUE_NAME = "order:mq:queue";</span><br><span class="line">    // 路由键</span><br><span class="line">    public final static String ROUTING_KEY = "order:mq:routing:key";</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    /**</span><br><span class="line">     * channel链接工厂</span><br><span class="line">     */</span><br><span class="line">    @Autowired</span><br><span class="line">    private CachingConnectionFactory connectionFactory;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    /**</span><br><span class="line">     * 监听器容器配置</span><br><span class="line">     */</span><br><span class="line">    @Autowired</span><br><span class="line">    private SimpleRabbitListenerContainerFactoryConfigurer factoryConfigurer;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    /**</span><br><span class="line">     * 声明rabbittemplate</span><br><span class="line">     * @return</span><br><span class="line">     */</span><br><span class="line">    @Bean</span><br><span class="line">    public RabbitTemplate rabbitTemplate(){</span><br><span class="line">        //消息发送成功确认，对应application.properties中的spring.rabbitmq.publisher-confirms=true</span><br><span class="line">        connectionFactory.setPublisherConfirms(true);</span><br><span class="line">        //消息发送失败确认，对应application.properties中的spring.rabbitmq.publisher-returns=true</span><br><span class="line">        connectionFactory.setPublisherReturns(true);</span><br><span class="line">        RabbitTemplate rabbitTemplate = new RabbitTemplate(connectionFactory);</span><br><span class="line">        //设置消息发送格式为json</span><br><span class="line">        rabbitTemplate.setMessageConverter(new Jackson2JsonMessageConverter());</span><br><span class="line">        rabbitTemplate.setMandatory(true);</span><br><span class="line">        //消息发送到exchange回调 需设置：spring.rabbitmq.publisher-confirms=true</span><br><span class="line">        rabbitTemplate.setConfirmCallback(new RabbitTemplate.ConfirmCallback() {</span><br><span class="line">            @Override</span><br><span class="line">            public void confirm(CorrelationData correlationData, boolean ack, String cause) {</span><br><span class="line">                logger.info("消息发送成功:correlationData({}),ack({}),cause({})",correlationData,ack,cause);</span><br><span class="line">            }</span><br><span class="line">        });</span><br><span class="line">        //消息从exchange发送到queue失败回调  需设置：spring.rabbitmq.publisher-returns=true</span><br><span class="line">        rabbitTemplate.setReturnCallback(new RabbitTemplate.ReturnCallback() {</span><br><span class="line">            @Override</span><br><span class="line">            public void returnedMessage(Message message, int replyCode, String replyText, String exchange, String routingKey) {</span><br><span class="line">                logger.info("消息丢失:exchange({}),route({}),replyCode({}),replyText({}),message:{}",exchange,routingKey,replyCode,replyText,message);</span><br><span class="line">            }</span><br><span class="line">        });</span><br><span class="line">        return rabbitTemplate;</span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    //---------------------------------------订单队列------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    /**</span><br><span class="line">     * 声明订单队列的交换机</span><br><span class="line">     * @return</span><br><span class="line">     */</span><br><span class="line">    @Bean</span><br><span class="line">    public TopicExchange orderTopicExchange(){</span><br><span class="line">        //设置为持久化 不自动删除</span><br><span class="line">        return new TopicExchange(EXCHANGE_NAME,true,false);</span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    /**</span><br><span class="line">     * 声明订单队列</span><br><span class="line">     * @return</span><br><span class="line">     */</span><br><span class="line">    @Bean</span><br><span class="line">    public Queue orderQueue(){</span><br><span class="line">        return new Queue(QUEUE_NAME,true);</span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    /**</span><br><span class="line">     * 将队列绑定到交换机</span><br><span class="line">     * @return</span><br><span class="line">     */</span><br><span class="line">    @Bean</span><br><span class="line">    public Binding simpleBinding(){</span><br><span class="line">        return BindingBuilder.bind(orderQueue()).to(orderTopicExchange()).with(ROUTING_KEY);</span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 生产消息</span><br><span class="line">public String send(String message){</span><br><span class="line">    rabbitTemplate.convertAndSend(RabbitConfig.EXCHANGE_NAME,RabbitConfig.ROUTING_KEY,message);</span><br><span class="line">    retuen "消息发送成功";</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// 配置rabbitmq监听</span><br><span class="line">/**</span><br><span class="line"> * 处理接收到的消息</span><br><span class="line"> * @param message 消息体</span><br><span class="line"> * @param channel 通道，确认消费用</span><br><span class="line"> */</span><br><span class="line">@RabbitListener(queues = RabbitConfig.QUEUE_NAME)</span><br><span class="line">public void onMessage(Message message, com.rabbitmq.client.Channel channel){</span><br><span class="line">    try{</span><br><span class="line">        //获取交付tag</span><br><span class="line">        long tag = message.getMessageProperties().getDeliveryTag();</span><br><span class="line">        String str = new String(message.getBody(),"utf-8");</span><br><span class="line">        logger.info("接收到的消息：{}",str);</span><br><span class="line">        //确认消费</span><br><span class="line">        channel.basicAck(tag,true);</span><br><span class="line">    }catch(Exception e){</span><br><span class="line">        logger.error("消息监听确认机制发生异常：",e.fillInStackTrace());</span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="并发配置"><a href="#并发配置" class="headerlink" title="并发配置"></a>并发配置</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/**</span><br><span class="line">   * 容器工厂配置 并发</span><br><span class="line">   * @return</span><br><span class="line">*/</span><br><span class="line">@Bean("containerFactory")</span><br><span class="line">public RabbitListenerContainerFactory rabbitListenerContainerFactory(ConnectionFactory connectionFactory){</span><br><span class="line">    SimpleRabbitListenerContainerFactory listenerContainerFactory = new SimpleRabbitListenerContainerFactory();</span><br><span class="line">    listenerContainerFactory.setConnectionFactory(connectionFactory);</span><br><span class="line">    listenerContainerFactory.setMessageConverter(new Jackson2JsonMessageConverter());</span><br><span class="line">    // 最大并发数</span><br><span class="line">    listenerContainerFactory.setMaxConcurrentConsumers(20);</span><br><span class="line">    // 初始并发数</span><br><span class="line">    listenerContainerFactory.setConcurrentConsumers(10);</span><br><span class="line">    return listenerContainerFactory;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// containerFactory 指定容器工厂</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@RabbitListener(queues = RabbitConfig.QUEUE_NAME,containerFactory = "containerFactory")</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
